# Environment Variables — Support Ticket Management System
#
# This project uses per-app .env files (not a single root .env).
# Copy the example files below before running locally.
#
#   backend/.env.example  →  backend/.env
#   frontend/.env.example →  frontend/.env
#
# Never commit real .env files. Only .env.example belongs in git.

# --- Backend (see backend/.env.example) ---
# PORT=3001
# MONGODB_URI=mongodb://localhost:27017/support_tickets
# CORS_ORIGIN=http://localhost:5173

# --- Frontend (see frontend/.env.example) ---
# VITE_API_URL=http://localhost:3001/api
